      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine with its signature individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain delivers a linear torque curve through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a M-variable limited-slip differential. Recent mechanical attention includes a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed suspension bushings to ensure the chassis remains rigid and communicative. The MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear geometry provide exceptional turn-in and lateral grip. This vehicle offers a pure mechanical connection for the discerning enthusiast seeking a well-sorted legendary performance platform.",
